    stable 0.9.5
   require curl gtk+
  optional gpsd '' --disable-realtime-gps-tracking for realtime GPS tracking feature
  category GPS
 attribute x11
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL viking/viking-$VERSION.tar.gz
  homepage http://viking.sf.net/
      opts --enable-static=no
  estimate 800
      desc 'viking is a gtk GPS data editor and viewer.
It can download and show Terraserver maps,
import and draw tracks and waypoints over them,
add coordinate lines, make new tracks and waypoints,
hide different things, and more.
It uses a hierarchical layering system to organize GPS data,
maps, and other layer types with spatial data (such as coordinate lines).'
